modvm
============

modvm is a cross-platform virtual machine hypervisor. This is only a demo version.

How to Build
-----------

It is recommended to build through CMake and Ninja. GNU Make is also needed to build the firmware. Tested versions are:

* CMake: 4.2.3
* Ninja: 1.13.2
* GNU Make: 4.4.1

First, create a build folder and enter it:

`mkdir build && cd build`

Then, run the following command to build modvm:

`CC=<your-cc> cmake -G Ninja .. && ninja`

The executable should then locate in `build/src/`, along with tests located in `build/tests/`.

To build the firmware, run `make` in `firmware/`.

Run the Demo
-----------

Make sure you are in the `build/` folder. Then:

`./src/modvm -m 1 -smp 3 -kernel ../firmware/boot.bin`